name: Milk Protein Fiber (Silk Latte)
description:
This listing is for 1 oz. of awesome milk protein fiber, undyed. Sooo wonderful and soft. Takes dye beautifully, my new favorite fiber. If you are interested in a larger or smaller quantity just let me know and I will change the listing for you. If you have never tried milk, just ask for a sample when you order something from my shop, this stuff is really to good not to try.

BUYER BEWARE: With the spike in popularity of milk protein fiber, a lower quality version of it has been brought onto the market. Rest assured that the milk fiber that I offer in my store is of the highest and silkiest quality available, you can purchase my milk fiber with confidence.

For a full selection of handdyed spinning fibers and handspun yarn (or just to check out my feedback) please see my etsy shop at www.punkjordane.etsy.com
